- ðŸ—‚ï¸ Provides [comprehensive project management](#projects), with a
  [universal lockfile](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/concepts/projects/layout#the-lockfile).
- â‡ï¸ [Runs scripts](#scripts), with support for
